 However, they\nremain bound for all values of the parameter $c$ considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2016 16:53:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Nov 2016 08:26:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
