tions to Witten's\nSU(2) anomaly are made. These observations may also be useful for numerical\nsimulations of topological surface states and of Dirac fermions without fermion\ndoubling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2016 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Dec 2017 19:02:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-29"}
