le is an\ninteresting alternative to empirical profiles and ad hoc fitting-functions that\nattempt to couple the asymptotic NFW decline with the inner core in SFDM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2016 20:12:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2016 15:42:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 30 Apr 2017 01:12:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-08"}
